WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:05.305 --> 00:00:07.073 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: UP NEXT, A
BULLET-RIDDLED CAR, A MISSING

00:00:07.106 --> 00:00:08.441 size:78% position:39%
DRIVER, AND NO WITNESSES.

00:00:08.474 --> 00:00:11.644 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; IT WOULD SEEM THAT SHE WAS
STILL ALIVE WHEN SHE WAS REMOVED

00:00:11.677 --> 00:00:12.812 align:start position:0%
FROM THE CAR.

00:00:12.845 --> 00:00:15.782
&gt;&gt; WHO WOULD DO SUCH A THING
LIKE THIS ON A PUBLIC ROADWAY?

00:00:15.815 --> 00:00:19.052 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: WAS IT AN AMBUSH
OR A RANDOM ATTACK?

00:00:19.085 --> 00:00:21.888 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; THIS IS MY DEFENSELESS LITTLE
GIRL WHO HAD BEEN SHOT AT.

00:00:21.921 --> 00:00:23.856 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; IT WAS A HEAD-SCRATCHER FROM
THE GET-GO.

00:00:23.889 --> 00:00:26.993 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: SOME TINY EVIDENCE
PROVIDES THE ANSWER.

00:00:27.026 --> 00:00:29.262 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; IT WAS ON HER SKIN, ON HER
JACKET.

00:00:29.295 --> 00:00:31.297
YOU CAN'T GET RID OF THIS STUFF.

00:00:39.805 --> 00:00:42.975 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: IN SOUTHERN
CALIFORNIA, LIKE ELSEWHERE IN

00:00:43.008 --> 00:00:45.878 align:start position:0%
THE UNITED STATES, VIRTUALLY
EVERYONE CELEBRATES

00:00:45.911 --> 00:00:47.814 align:start position:0%
INDEPENDENCE DAY.

00:00:47.847 --> 00:00:51.851 align:start position:0%
SOME CELEBRATE A LITTLE TOO
MUCH.

00:00:51.884 --> 00:00:55.788
THAT'S WHAT POLICE THOUGHT WHEN
THEY FOUND A DESERTED CAR AROUND

00:00:55.821 --> 00:00:59.225 align:start position:0%
4:00 IN THE MORNING, WITH THE
ENGINE STILL RUNNING, OFF

00:00:59.258 --> 00:01:03.062 align:start position:0%
ROUTE 118, JUST NORTH OF
LOS ANGELES.

00:01:03.095 --> 00:01:06.766 line:0%
&gt;&gt; A LOT OF PEOPLE THOUGHT THAT
MAYBE SOMEBODY WAS DRUNK AND

00:01:06.799 --> 00:01:09.735 align:start position:0% line:0%
THEY HAD ABANDONED THEIR CAR
ALONGSIDE THE ROAD.

00:01:09.768 --> 00:01:13.573 line:0%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: BUT A CLOSER LOOK
REVEALED SOMETHING MORE SERIOUS.

00:01:13.606 --> 00:01:16.742 line:0%
&gt;&gt; WE HAD SEVERAL BULLETS THAT
HAD WENT THROUGH THE WINDSHIELD

00:01:16.775 --> 00:01:19.745 align:start position:0% line:0%
INTO THE VEHICLE, AND TWO
ADDITIONAL BULLETS THAT HAD WENT

00:01:19.778 --> 00:01:21.814 line:0%
THROUGH THE SIDE OF THE VEHICLE.

00:01:21.847 --> 00:01:25.284 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: A WOMAN'S SHOE WAS
INSIDE THE CAR.

00:01:25.317 --> 00:01:27.386 align:start position:0%
ANOTHER WAS OUTSIDE.

00:01:27.419 --> 00:01:31.858 align:start position:0%
BLOOD WAS ON THE STEERING WHEEL,
THE DRIVER'S SEAT, AND

00:01:31.891 --> 00:01:33.626 align:start position:0%
FLOORBOARD.

00:01:33.659 --> 00:01:36.863 align:start position:0%
POLICE FANNED OUT ALL OVER THE
AREA.

00:01:36.896 --> 00:01:40.633 align:start position:0%
THERE WAS NO BLOOD TRAIL, NO
VICTIM.

00:01:40.666 --> 00:01:43.870 line:0%
&gt;&gt; IT WAS HIGHLY UNUSUAL FOR US
TO HAVE A VIOLENT-CRIME SCENE

00:01:43.903 --> 00:01:46.639 align:start position:0% line:0%
LIKE THAT WHERE THE VICTIM WAS
MISSING.

00:01:46.672 --> 00:01:50.409 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: THE CAR WAS A
RENTAL AND HAD BEEN LEASED THAT

00:01:50.442 --> 00:01:54.013 align:start position:0%
DAY TO MEGAN BARROSO, A
20-YEAR-OLD COLLEGE STUDENT WHO

00:01:54.046 --> 00:01:55.014 align:start position:0%
LIVED NEARBY.

00:01:55.047 --> 00:01:58.050
HER PURSE WAS COVERED IN BLOOD.

00:01:58.083 --> 00:01:59.752 size:78% position:39%
HER CELLPHONE WAS INSIDE.

00:01:59.785 --> 00:02:06.726
IT LOOKED AS IF SHE HAD TRIED TO
USE HER PHONE TO CALL FOR HELP.

00:02:06.759 --> 00:02:10.530 line:0%
&gt;&gt; SHE HAD GONE TO A FOURTH OF
JULY PARTY WITH HER BEST FRIEND

00:02:10.563 --> 00:02:14.667 size:81% position:41% line:0%
AND OTHER YOUNG PEOPLE, I
BELIEVE IN THE BEACH AREA.

00:02:14.700 --> 00:02:18.070 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: ACCORDING TO
FRIENDS, MEGAN LEFT THE PARTY

00:02:18.103 --> 00:02:22.441 align:start position:0%
ALONE AT 2:45 A.M., A LITTLE
MORE THAN AN HOUR BEFORE HER CAR

00:02:22.474 --> 00:02:23.976 align:start position:0%
WAS FOUND.

00:02:24.009 --> 00:02:27.613 align:start position:0%
POLICE CHECKED LOCAL HOSPITALS,
BUT NO ONE MATCHING MEGAN'S

00:02:27.646 --> 00:02:29.682 size:84% position:42%
DESCRIPTION HAD CHECKED IN.

00:02:29.715 --> 00:02:32.451 line:0%
&gt;&gt; WE DIDN'T KNOW IF THIS PERSON
WAS EITHER DEAD OR ALIVE AT THAT

00:02:32.484 --> 00:02:33.619 align:start position:0% line:0%
POINT.

00:02:33.652 --> 00:02:35.721 line:0%
THERE WAS A SIGNIFICANT AMOUNT
OF BLOOD IN THE CAR, BUT NOT

00:02:35.754 --> 00:02:39.225 size:81% position:41% line:0%
ENOUGH TO SUGGEST THAT THE
PERSON WAS, IN FACT, DEAD.

00:02:39.258 --> 00:02:42.028 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; MY DAUGHTER WAS OUT THERE
SOMEWHERE, AND I WAS HOPING THAT

00:02:42.061 --> 00:02:46.032 align:start position:0%
I WOULD GET A CALL FROM HER ANY
DAY, ANY MINUTE.

00:02:46.065 --> 00:02:48.367 align:start position:0%
NO CALL CAME.

00:02:48.400 --> 00:02:53.072
&gt;&gt; Narrator: INVESTIGATORS FOUND
FIVE SHELL CASINGS AT THE END OF

00:02:53.105 --> 00:02:56.909 align:start position:0%
THE EXIT RAMP AND ANOTHER ABOUT
200 FEET AWAY.

00:02:56.942 --> 00:03:00.947
&gt;&gt; OUR FORENSIC PEOPLE WERE ABLE
TO TELL US THAT IT MOST LIKELY

00:03:00.980 --> 00:03:06.786 align:start position:0%
WAS AN AK-47-TYPE RIFLE -- AN
ASSAULT RIFLE.

00:03:06.819 --> 00:03:11.123 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; KNOWING THAT MEGAN HAD BEEN
ASSAULTED WITH THIS AK-47,

00:03:11.156 --> 00:03:17.296 align:start position:0%
AGAIN, JUST SENT CHILLS OF
AGONY THROUGH MY MIND.

00:03:17.329 --> 00:03:21.801
&gt;&gt; Narrator: INVESTIGATORS ALSO
NOTICED A FRESH SCRAPE ALONG THE

00:03:21.834 --> 00:03:24.704 size:78% position:39%
DRIVER'S SIDE OF THE CAR.

00:03:24.737 --> 00:03:30.009 align:start position:0%
IT LOOKED AS IF MEGAN'S CAR HAD
BEEN SIDESWIPED.

00:03:30.042 --> 00:03:33.980 align:start position:0%
THEN INVESTIGATORS GOT A HUGE
BREAK.

00:03:34.013 --> 00:03:38.084
THEY LEARNED THAT MEGAN'S RENTAL
CAR WAS ONE OF THE FIRST TO BE

00:03:38.117 --> 00:03:41.220 align:start position:0%
EQUIPPED WITH AN EVENT-DATA
RECORDER.

00:03:41.253 --> 00:03:44.023
&gt;&gt; THE EVENT-DATA RECORDER IS A
HUGE STEP FORWARD IN TRAFFIC

00:03:44.056 --> 00:03:45.157 align:start position:0%
SAFETY.

00:03:45.191 --> 00:03:47.393 align:start position:0% line:0%
IT'S LIKE THE BLACK BOX IN AN
AIRCRAFT THAT GIVES US AN

00:03:47.426 --> 00:03:50.463 align:start position:0% line:0%
OPPORTUNITY TO BETTER UNDERSTAND
HOW CRASHES HAPPEN.

00:03:50.496 --> 00:03:54.967 size:88% position:44%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: THE RECORDER, A
SMALL ON-BOARD COMPUTER, IS

00:03:55.000 --> 00:03:56.168 align:start position:0%
ALWAYS ON.

00:03:56.201 --> 00:04:00.406 align:start position:0%
IN THE EVENT OF A CRASH, IT
AUTOMATICALLY SAVES THE PREVIOUS

00:04:00.439 --> 00:04:03.242 size:88% position:44%
FIVE SECONDS OF INFORMATION.

00:04:03.275 --> 00:04:08.481
WHEN MEGAN'S CAR HIT THE MEDIAN,
IT ACTIVATED THE DATA RECORDER.

00:04:08.514 --> 00:04:13.185
IT REVEALED THAT FIVE SECONDS
EARLIER, MEGAN'S CAR WAS AT A

00:04:13.218 --> 00:04:14.487 align:start position:0%
COMPLETE STOP.

00:04:14.520 --> 00:04:16.455 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; I THINK HE STARTED SHOOTING
AT HER.

00:04:16.488 --> 00:04:19.458
SHE WAS PROBABLY DUCKING, BUT AT
SOME POINT, SHE REALIZED, "I'D

00:04:19.491 --> 00:04:20.926 size:78% position:39%
BETTER GET OUT OF THERE."

00:04:20.959 --> 00:04:24.997
&gt;&gt; Narrator: THE RECORDER SHOWED
MEGAN FLOORED THE ACCELERATOR.

00:04:25.030 --> 00:04:26.699 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; SHE WENT TO 100% OPEN
THROTTLE.

00:04:26.732 --> 00:04:29.568
SHE JAMMED THAT GAS PEDAL TO THE
FLOOR, AND SHE TRIED TO GET OUT

00:04:29.601 --> 00:04:30.802 align:start position:0%
OF THERE.

00:04:30.836 --> 00:04:35.174 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: BLOOD INSIDE THE
CAR SHOWED MEGAN WAS WOUNDED AND

00:04:35.207 --> 00:04:37.009 align:start position:0%
POSSIBLY STILL ALIVE.

00:04:37.042 --> 00:04:39.278 align:start position:0%
BUT WHERE WAS SHE?

00:04:39.311 --> 00:04:41.180 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; WE KNEW WE HAD A BODY
SOMEWHERE.

00:04:41.213 --> 00:04:43.182 size:81% position:41%
WE JUST COULDN'T FIND HER.

00:04:45.317 --> 00:04:48.954
&gt;&gt; Narrator: AS POLICE SEARCHED
FOR 20-YEAR-OLD MEGAN BARROSO,

00:04:48.987 --> 00:04:52.425
THEY TRIED TO RECONSTRUCT HER
ACTIVITIES ON THE NIGHT OF HER

00:04:52.458 --> 00:04:54.727 align:start position:0%
DISAPPEARANCE.

00:04:54.760 --> 00:04:59.131 align:start position:0%
HER FRIENDS SAID SHE LEFT A
FOURTH OF JULY PARTY AT 2:45 IN

00:04:59.164 --> 00:05:01.133 size:81% position:41%
THE MORNING AND WAS ALONE.

00:05:01.166 --> 00:05:05.705
HER ABANDONED CAR WAS FOUND AT
THE BOTTOM OF AN EXIT RAMP OFF A

00:05:05.738 --> 00:05:09.809 align:start position:0%
DESERTED STRETCH OF HIGHWAY
ABOUT AN HOUR LATER.

00:05:09.842 --> 00:05:12.912 line:0%
&gt;&gt; WE FOUND THAT MEGAN DIDN'T
HAVE ANY BOYFRIEND PROBLEMS.

00:05:12.945 --> 00:05:15.581 align:start position:0% line:0%
SHE DIDN'T HAVE ANYONE THAT WAS
UPSET WITH HER.

00:05:15.614 --> 00:05:17.183 line:0%
IN FACT, IT WAS THE OPPOSITE.

00:05:17.216 --> 00:05:19.552 align:start position:0% line:0%
EVERYBODY LIKED MEGAN.

00:05:19.585 --> 00:05:23.255
&gt;&gt; Narrator: SOMEONE HAD FIRED
MULTIPLE SHOTS INTO MEGAN'S CAR

00:05:23.288 --> 00:05:28.227 align:start position:0%
WITH WHAT INVESTIGATORS BELIEVED
WAS AN AK-47 ASSAULT RIFLE.

00:05:28.260 --> 00:05:32.164 align:start position:0%
TO RE-CREATE THE SHOOTING,
ANALYSTS USED LASERS TO

00:05:32.197 --> 00:05:35.801 align:start position:0%
DETERMINE WHERE THE SHOOTER WAS
STANDING.

00:05:35.834 --> 00:05:39.839 align:start position:0% line:0%
&gt;&gt; WE USE A LASER BEAM BECAUSE
IT'S A NICE, STRAIGHT LIGHT

00:05:39.872 --> 00:05:44.243 line:0%
BEAM THAT WE CAN JUST PROJECT
THROUGH A NUMBER OF HOLES.

00:05:44.276 --> 00:05:46.545 size:88% position:44%
AND IT MAKES A GOOD DISPLAY.

00:05:46.578 --> 00:05:51.150
IT ALLOWS US TO SEE WHERE THE
BULLET HAS PASSED THROUGH,

00:05:51.183 --> 00:05:52.718 size:81% position:41%
WHAT IT'S INTERACTED WITH.

00:05:52.751 --> 00:05:56.622
&gt;&gt; Narrator: THE LASER ANALYSIS
SHOWED THE SHOOTER STOOD 60 FEET

00:05:56.655 --> 00:06:00.793
AWAY FROM MEGAN'S CAR WHEN HE
STARTED FIRING, AND HE CLOSED

00:06:00.826 --> 00:06:04.130 size:88% position:44%
THE DISTANCE WITH EACH SHOT.

00:06:04.163 --> 00:06:06.298 align:start position:0%
ONE SHOT HIT THE HOOD.

00:06:06.331 --> 00:06:09.068 size:78% position:39%
THREE HIT THE WINDSHIELD.

00:06:09.101 --> 00:06:11.871 align:start position:0%
ANOTHER HIT THE DRIVER'S-SIDE
DOOR.

00:06:11.904 --> 00:06:15.875
INVESTIGATORS CONCLUDED THE SHOT
FIRED THROUGH THE PASSENGER-SIDE

00:06:15.908 --> 00:06:18.344
DOOR HAPPENED SOMEWHERE ELSE.

00:06:18.377 --> 00:06:20.880 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; IT CAME IN FROM A COMPLETELY
DIFFERENT DIRECTION.

00:06:20.913 --> 00:06:23.616
IT COULDN'T HAVE BEEN PART OF
THE SAME SERIES OF GUNFIRE

00:06:23.649 --> 00:06:26.719 align:start position:0%
WITHOUT A DRAMATIC CHANGE IN THE
POSITION OF THE SHOOTER.

00:06:26.752 --> 00:06:30.456 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: THIS GUNSHOT, ALONG
WITH THE SIDESWIPE ON MEGAN'S

00:06:30.489 --> 00:06:34.193 align:start position:0%
CAR, LED ANALYSTS TO CONCLUDE
THIS ALTERCATION HAPPENED ON THE

00:06:34.226 --> 00:06:35.428 align:start position:0%
HIGHWAY.

00:06:35.461 --> 00:06:39.365 align:start position:0%
WITH THE LASER INFORMATION AND
EVENT-DATA RECORDER,

00:06:39.398 --> 00:06:44.036
INVESTIGATORS PUT TOGETHER THIS
ANIMATION OF WHAT THEY THOUGHT

00:06:44.069 --> 00:06:45.270 align:start position:0%
HAPPENED.

00:06:45.304 --> 00:06:49.809
IT WAS CLEAR -- SOMEONE TRIED TO
FORCE MEGAN OFF THE HIGHWAY BY

00:06:49.842 --> 00:06:51.644 align:start position:0%
SIDESWIPING HER CAR.

00:06:51.677 --> 00:06:56.048
THEN MEGAN'S ATTACKER MOVED TO
THE PASSENGER SIDE AND FIRED

00:06:56.081 --> 00:06:57.650 align:start position:0%
INTO HER BACKSEAT.

00:06:57.683 --> 00:07:01.520 size:88% position:44%
AS MEGAN DROVE OFF THE EXIT
RAMP, HER ATTACKER MUST HAVE

00:07:01.553 --> 00:07:06.225
SPED IN FRONT OF HER, BLOCKED
HER PATH, AND STARTED SHOOTING.

00:07:06.258 --> 00:07:08.227 align:start position:0%
THERE WERE FOUR SHOTS.

00:07:08.260 --> 00:07:10.429 size:88% position:44%
SHE FLOORED THE ACCELERATOR.

00:07:10.462 --> 00:07:14.667 align:start position:0%
A FIFTH SHOT WENT THROUGH THE
SIDE DOOR AND HIT MEGAN.

00:07:14.700 --> 00:07:17.803 align:start position:0%
THE BLOOD EVIDENCE SHOWS MEGAN
TRIED TO REACH FOR HER

00:07:17.836 --> 00:07:20.005 align:start position:0%
CELLPHONE, POSSIBLY TO CALL
POLICE.

00:07:20.038 --> 00:07:24.276 align:start position:0%
HER CAR HIT THE MEDIAN.

00:07:24.309 --> 00:07:28.380 align:start position:0%
THE ASSAILANT APPARENTLY DRAGGED
HER INTO ANOTHER VEHICLE AND

00:07:28.413 --> 00:07:30.049 align:start position:0%
DROVE AWAY.

00:07:30.082 --> 00:07:32.985 line:0%
&gt;&gt; YOU HAVE TO ASSUME THAT THE
PERSON THAT CARRIED OUT THIS

00:07:33.018 --> 00:07:37.857 align:start position:0% line:0%
CRIME WAS VERY BOLD, VERY MUCH
A RISK-TAKER.

00:07:37.890 --> 00:07:42.094 line:0%
&gt;&gt; THERE WERE QUESTIONS ABOUT
WHO WOULD DO SUCH A THING LIKE

00:07:42.127 --> 00:07:49.768 line:0%
THIS ON A PUBLIC ROADWAY, AND
118 IS A VERY PUBLIC ROADWAY.

00:07:49.801 --> 00:07:54.039 align:start position:0% line:0%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: THE BLOOD INSIDE
THE CAR MEANT MEGAN WAS WOUNDED,

00:07:54.072 --> 00:07:57.643 align:start position:0% line:0%
BUT WAS PROBABLY STILL ALIVE
WHEN SHE WAS ABDUCTED.

00:07:57.676 --> 00:08:01.747 align:start position:0% line:0%
&gt;&gt; AT THAT POINT, I REALIZED
THAT MY DAUGHTER WAS IN HORRIBLE

00:08:01.780 --> 00:08:05.351 align:start position:0% line:0%
TROUBLE, THAT THIS WAS NOT A
GOOD SITUATION.

00:08:05.384 --> 00:08:10.890 align:start position:0%
AND THIS WAS A REAL BIG, BAD
THING THAT WAS HAPPENING.

00:08:10.923 --> 00:08:14.193 size:88% position:44%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: THE SHERIFF'S
DEPARTMENT, ALONG WITH OTHER

00:08:14.226 --> 00:08:17.696 align:start position:0%
LAW-ENFORCEMENT AGENCIES,
OFFERED A REWARD FOR INFORMATION

00:08:17.729 --> 00:08:19.365 align:start position:0%
LEADING TO AN ARREST.

00:08:19.398 --> 00:08:24.637
BUT THREE LONG WEEKS PASSED WITH
NO LEADS ON MEGAN'S ABDUCTION.

00:08:24.670 --> 00:08:28.774 align:start position:0%
THEN A SIMI VALLEY RESIDENT
CALLED POLICE WITH SOME

00:08:28.807 --> 00:08:30.576 align:start position:0%
INFORMATION.

00:08:30.609 --> 00:08:35.247 size:84% position:42%
HE SAID HE FOUND A HOMEMADE
VIDEOTAPE IN HIS ROOMMATE'S

00:08:35.280 --> 00:08:40.386 align:start position:0%
TRASH SHOWING SEXUAL ACTS SO
HORRIFYING, HE KNEW IT NEEDED TO

00:08:40.419 --> 00:08:43.822 align:start position:0%
BE REPORTED TO POLICE.

00:08:43.855 --> 00:08:48.360 align:start position:0% line:0%
&gt;&gt; LO AND BEHOLD, HERE'S THIS
GUY RAPING THESE WOMEN.

00:08:48.393 --> 00:08:53.232
&gt;&gt; Narrator: THE MAN SAID HE HAD
NO DOUBT THE RAPIST ON THE TAPE

00:08:53.265 --> 00:08:57.770
WAS HIS ROOMMATE, 30-YEAR-OLD
VINCENT SANCHEZ, AN ELECTRICIAN

00:08:57.803 --> 00:09:01.740 align:start position:0%
WHO WORKED IN THE LOCAL FILM
INDUSTRY.

00:09:01.773 --> 00:09:07.246 align:start position:0%
THE TAPE SHOWED SANCHEZ RAPING
NUMEROUS WOMEN ON-CAMERA.

00:09:07.279 --> 00:09:11.784 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; IT WAS QUITE HORRIFYING TO
ACTUALLY SEE A WOMAN BEING RAPED

00:09:11.817 --> 00:09:13.586 align:start position:0%
AND SEXUALLY ASSAULTED.

00:09:13.619 --> 00:09:16.989
&gt;&gt; Narrator: WHEN INVESTIGATORS
ASKED SANCHEZ'S ROOMMATE WHETHER

00:09:17.022 --> 00:09:21.894
ANYONE IN THE HOUSE OWNED AN
ASSAULT RIFLE, HE SAID HE DID.

00:09:21.927 --> 00:09:24.563
&gt;&gt; I'M SITTING ON THE BED, AND
HE TELLS ME, "WELL, YEAH, THE

00:09:24.596 --> 00:09:25.431 align:start position:0%
GUN'S RIGHT HERE.

00:09:25.464 --> 00:09:26.799 size:78% position:39%
IT'S UNDERNEATH THE BED."

00:09:26.832 --> 00:09:29.668
AND AS SOON AS I LOOKED AT IT,
THE HAIR ON THE BACK OF MY NECK

00:09:29.701 --> 00:09:31.337 align:start position:0%
STOOD UP.

00:09:31.370 --> 00:09:35.140
&gt;&gt; Narrator: IT WAS AN AK-47.

00:09:35.173 --> 00:09:39.078 align:start position:0%
DETECTIVES ALSO FOUND SOMETHING
NEAR THE TRASH OUTSIDE THE

00:09:39.111 --> 00:09:40.613 align:start position:0%
HOUSE.

00:09:40.646 --> 00:09:44.350
&gt;&gt; I EXCUSED MYSELF FROM THE
INTERVIEW TO TAKE A PHONE CALL,

00:09:44.383 --> 00:09:48.087 size:84% position:42%
AND I WALKED OUTSIDE THE
RESIDENCE, AND OVER BY SOME

00:09:48.120 --> 00:09:52.558 align:start position:0%
TRASH CANS, I SAW A GARMENT OF
CLOTHING ON THE GROUND AND

00:09:52.591 --> 00:09:54.326 align:start position:0%
WALKED UP TO IT.

00:09:54.359 --> 00:09:56.762 align:start position:0%
AND I SAW THAT IT WAS A GREEN
JACKET.

00:09:56.795 --> 00:09:59.698 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; IT WAS A GREEN GAP JACKET
WITH AN ORANGE LINING.

00:09:59.731 --> 00:10:01.667 size:81% position:41%
IT WAS FAIRLY DISTINCTIVE.

00:10:01.700 --> 00:10:04.970
AND HE SAW WHAT HE BELIEVED TO
BE A BULLET HOLE IN THE SIDE.

00:10:05.003 --> 00:10:08.374 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: IT WAS THE
SAME-COLOR JACKET MEGAN BARROSO

00:10:08.407 --> 00:10:12.845 align:start position:0%
WORE ON THE NIGHT SHE WAS
ABDUCTED.

00:10:12.878 --> 00:10:17.716 align:start position:0%
WAS IT POSSIBLE MEGAN WAS STILL
ALIVE?

00:10:20.052 --> 00:10:23.055 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: JUST DAYS AFTER
INVESTIGATORS FOUND

00:10:23.088 --> 00:10:26.859
MEGAN BARROSO'S GREEN JACKET IN
