ASSAULTED.

00:11:17.075 --> 00:11:21.013
&gt;&gt; Narrator: IT LOOKED AS IF
MEGAN WAS STILL ALIVE WHEN SHE

00:11:21.046 --> 00:11:23.315 align:start position:0%
