00:11:33.558 --> 00:11:36.929
&gt;&gt; Narrator: THEN THE MEDICAL
EXAMINER NOTICED SOMETHING

00:11:36.962 --> 00:11:39.231 align:start position:0%
UNUSUAL -- RED GLITTER.

00:11:39.264 --> 00:11:43.102 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; WHAT THEY CALL "PIXIE DUST"
IN MEGAN'S HAIR AND ON HER

00:11:43.135 --> 00:11:43.902 align:start position:0%
CLOTHING.

00:11:43.935 --> 00:11:46.371 align:start position:0%
AND IT WAS RED GLITTER, IN
ESSENCE.

00:11:46.404 --> 00:11:50.209 size:88% position:44%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: MEGAN'S GREEN
JACKET WAS FOUND OUTSIDE THE

00:11:50.242 --> 00:11:54.146 align:start position:0%
HOME OF VINCENT SANCHEZ, A
PART-TIME ELECTRICIAN WHO CAME

00:11:54.179 --> 00:11:58.484 align:start position:0%
TO POLICE ATTENTION WHEN HIS
ROOMMATE FOUND A HOMEMADE

00:11:58.517 --> 00:12:03.122 align:start position:0%
VIDEOTAPE OF SANCHEZ SEXUALLY
ASSAULTING SEVERAL WOMEN.

00:12:03.155 --> 00:12:07.159 align:start position:0%
WHEN POLICE STUDIED THE
VIDEOTAPE IN DETAIL, THEY

00:12:07.192 --> 00:12:11.663
DISCOVERED THE WOMEN WERE THE
VICTIMS OF THE SIMI VALLEY

00:12:11.696 --> 00:12:12.797 align:start position:0%
RAPIST.

00:12:12.831 --> 00:12:17.870 size:88% position:44%
15 UNSOLVED RAPES POLICE HAD
BEEN TRYING TO SOLVE FOR THE

00:12:17.903 --> 00:12:19.304 align:start position:0%
PAST 5 YEARS.

00:12:19.337 --> 00:12:24.276
&gt;&gt; THE PERPETRATOR WOULD BREAK
IN TO THE HOME OF THE VICTIMS,

00:12:24.309 --> 00:12:26.445 size:78% position:39%
PRIMARILY IN THE EVENING.

00:12:26.478 --> 00:12:31.884
SOME OF THE VICTIMS WERE YOUNG
TEENAGE GIRLS, 15, 16 YEARS OLD,

00:12:31.917 --> 00:12:37.089 align:start position:0%
WITH PARENTS SLEEPING IN ANOTHER
ROOM WITHIN THE HOUSEHOLD.

00:12:37.122 --> 00:12:41.393
&gt;&gt; Narrator: WHEN QUESTIONED BY
POLICE, SANCHEZ ADMITTED HE WAS

00:12:41.426 --> 00:12:45.297 size:88% position:44%
THE SIMI VALLEY RAPIST, BUT
DENIED HAVING ANYTHING TO DO

00:12:45.330 --> 00:12:47.399 size:88% position:44%
WITH MEGAN BARROSO'S MURDER.

00:12:47.432 --> 00:12:52.137 size:88% position:44% line:0%
&gt;&gt; VERY HESITANT TO ANSWER,
DIDN'T WANT TO TALK ANYMORE.

00:12:52.170 --> 00:12:55.107 line:0%
SAID HE DIDN'T KNOW HER, DIDN'T
KNOW WHAT I WAS TALKING ABOUT,

00:12:55.140 --> 00:12:57.176 size:88% position:44% line:0%
HAD NOTHING TO DO WITH THAT.

00:12:57.209 --> 00:13:00.679 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: INVESTIGATORS
SEARCHED SANCHEZ'S PICKUP TRUCK

00:13:00.712 --> 00:13:01.980 align:start position:0%
FOR POSSIBLE CLUES.

00:13:02.013 --> 00:13:06.485
IT WAS CLEAR THE TRUCK HAD BEEN
THOROUGHLY WASHED AND CLEANED.

00:13:06.518 --> 00:13:12.457
BUT TAPE LIFTS OF THE UPHOLSTERY
FOUND SOMETHING VERY DIFFICULT

00:13:12.490 --> 00:13:16.829 align:start position:0%
TO GET RID OF -- TINY SPECKS OF
RED GLITTER.

00:13:16.862 --> 00:13:21.333 size:88% position:44%
INVESTIGATORS ALSO FOUND RED
GLITTER IN THE GREEN JACKET

00:13:21.366 --> 00:13:23.702
FOUND OUTSIDE SANCHEZ'S HOME.

00:13:23.735 --> 00:13:28.640 align:start position:0%
THEY EVEN FOUND ONE MICROSCOPIC
SPECK ON THE AK-47 RIFLE

00:13:28.673 --> 00:13:32.444 align:start position:0%
SANCHEZ'S ROOMMATE TURNED OVER
TO POLICE.

00:13:32.477 --> 00:13:37.783 align:start position:0%
TO FIND OUT IF ALL THIS GLITTER
WAS FROM THE SAME SOURCE,

00:13:37.816 --> 00:13:42.321 size:75% position:38%
INVESTIGATORS SENT IT TO
EDWIN JONES, A FORENSIC

00:13:42.354 --> 00:13:46.825 align:start position:0%
SCIENTIST WITH ONE OF THE
LARGEST COLLECTIONS OF GLITTER

00:13:46.858 --> 00:13:51.063 align:start position:0%
IN THE WORLD, WITH CLOSE TO
1,000 SPECIMENS.

00:13:51.096 --> 00:13:54.633 line:0%
&gt;&gt; I HAVE AN UNUSUAL HOBBY OF
COLLECTING MICRO THINGS, AND

00:13:54.666 --> 00:13:57.603 line:0%
I'VE BEEN COLLECTING GLITTER FOR
MANY YEARS BEFORE THIS CASE, AND

00:13:57.636 --> 00:13:59.771 align:start position:0% line:0%
I'VE BEEN COLLECTING GLITTER
SINCE THIS CASE.

00:13:59.804 --> 00:14:05.077 line:0%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: UNDER A MICROSCOPE,
JONES DISCOVERED THAT THIS RED

00:14:05.110 --> 00:14:11.250 size:84% position:42% line:0%
GLITTER WAS A HEXAGON SHAPE
APPROXIMATELY 250 MICRONS.

00:14:11.283 --> 00:14:15.854 align:start position:0%
JONES KNEW IMMEDIATELY THAT THIS
WAS UNLIKE ANY OF THE

00:14:15.887 --> 00:14:19.057 align:start position:0%
RED-GLITTER SAMPLES HE'D EVER
SEEN.

00:14:19.090 --> 00:14:22.427
&gt;&gt; I FOUND OUT THAT THE GLITTER
HAD ONE LAYER OF ALUMINUM FOR

00:14:22.460 --> 00:14:23.661 align:start position:0%
REFLECTION.

00:14:23.695 --> 00:14:27.666
SO LITERALLY, THE PARTICLE WAS
ASYMMETRICAL, MEANING THAT IT'S

00:14:27.699 --> 00:14:29.534 size:84% position:42%
NOT THE SAME ON BOTH SIDES.

00:14:29.567 --> 00:14:32.738 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; IT'S RED ON ONE SIDE AND
SILVER ON THE OTHER.

00:14:32.771 --> 00:14:35.407 size:88% position:44% line:0%
IT WAS A VERY UNIQUE TYPE OF
GLITTER THAT JUST THIS ONE

00:14:35.440 --> 00:14:36.975 align:start position:0% line:0%
COMPANY HAD MADE.

00:14:37.008 --> 00:14:40.579
&gt;&gt; Narrator: JONES DISCOVERED
THAT THIS GLITTER WAS NOT A

00:14:40.612 --> 00:14:41.847 align:start position:0%
BEST-SELLING ITEM.

00:14:41.880 --> 00:14:45.918 align:start position:0%
ONLY 10,000 BOTTLES HAD EVER
BEEN MADE.

00:14:45.951 --> 00:14:50.255 align:start position:0%
INVESTIGATORS LEARNED THAT
DURING THE FOURTH OF JULY PARTY

00:14:50.288 --> 00:14:54.426 align:start position:0%
MEGAN ATTENDED, THE HOST THREW
RED GLITTER ON EVERYONE,

00:14:54.459 --> 00:14:55.794 align:start position:0%
INCLUDING MEGAN.

00:14:55.827 --> 00:14:57.362 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; THANKS.

00:14:57.395 --> 00:14:59.364 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; I SAID, "DO YOU STILL HAVE
THE BOTTLE?"

00:14:59.397 --> 00:15:00.532 align:start position:0%
SHE SAYS, "YES, I DO."

00:15:00.565 --> 00:15:03.669
SO WE THEN WENT AND RECOVERED
THE REMAINING PORTION OF THE

00:15:03.702 --> 00:15:04.670 align:start position:0%
GLITTER.

00:15:04.703 --> 00:15:08.173 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: SCIENTISTS
CONFIRMED THE GLITTER IN

00:15:08.206 --> 00:15:12.911
MEGAN BARROSO'S HAIR CAME FROM
MEGAN'S FRIEND, AND IT WAS THE

00:15:12.944 --> 00:15:18.784
SAME GLITTER FOUND IN SANCHEZ'S
TRUCK, ON THE AK-47 RIFLE, ON

00:15:18.817 --> 00:15:24.523 align:start position:0%
MEGAN'S JACKET FOUND IN
SANCHEZ'S TRASH, AND IN MEGAN'S

00:15:24.556 --> 00:15:25.724 align:start position:0%
OWN CAR.

00:15:25.757 --> 00:15:30.662 align:start position:0%
IT WAS THE ONLY PIECE OF
EVIDENCE THAT TIED SANCHEZ TO

00:15:30.695 --> 00:15:32.864 align:start position:0%
EVERYTHING.

00:15:32.897 --> 00:15:37.069 size:84% position:42%
INVESTIGATORS ALSO SEARCHED
SANCHEZ'S TRUCK FOR BLOOD.

00:15:37.102 --> 00:15:40.605
&gt;&gt; WHEN THE TECH PUT THE LUMINOL
ON THE INSIDE OF THE VEHICLE, IT

00:15:40.638 --> 00:15:42.240
LIT UP LIKE A CHRISTMAS TREE.

00:15:42.273 --> 00:15:47.346 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: DNA TESTING
REVEALED BLOOD ON THE PASSENGER

00:15:47.379 --> 00:15:49.014 align:start position:0%
SEAT WAS MEGAN'S.

00:15:49.047 --> 00:15:53.118 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; THERE WAS A HORIZONTAL
APPARENT BLOODSTAIN RIGHT IN

00:15:53.151 --> 00:15:57.322
THE AREA WHERE MEGAN'S WOUND WAS
TO HER SIDE, INDICATING THAT SHE

00:15:57.355 --> 00:16:01.994
HAD BEEN SITTING UPRIGHT IN THE
PASSENGER SEAT OF THAT TRUCK AT

00:16:02.027 --> 00:16:04.196
ONE POINT, SO SHE WASN'T DEAD.

00:16:04.229 --> 00:16:05.530 align:start position:0%
SHE WAS SITTING.

00:16:05.563 --> 00:16:09.601
&gt;&gt; Narrator: FORENSIC TESTS ON
THE SCRAPE MARK ON THE SIDE OF

00:16:09.634 --> 00:16:13.238 align:start position:0%
MEGAN'S CAR MATCHED THE PAINT
FROM SANCHEZ'S TRUCK.

00:16:13.271 --> 00:16:18.176
INVESTIGATORS TEST-FIRED THE
AK-47 AND COMPARED THE BULLETS

00:16:18.209 --> 00:16:21.213 align:start position:0%
TO FRAGMENTS FOUND WITH MEGAN'S
BODY.

00:16:21.246 --> 00:16:24.883 size:88% position:44% line:0%
&gt;&gt; WE TIED THAT RIFLE TO THE
CRIME SCENE AND TO THE BODY,

00:16:24.916 --> 00:16:28.687 line:0%
BOTH, WITH THE FRAGMENTS THAT
WERE TAKEN FROM THE CAR, FROM

00:16:28.720 --> 00:16:30.322 align:start position:0% line:0%
THE CRIME SCENE.

00:16:30.355 --> 00:16:36.028 align:start position:0%
CERTAINLY THAT HELPED TO TIE THE
RIFLE IN TO MR. SANCHEZ, AND

00:16:36.061 --> 00:16:39.264 align:start position:0%
MR. SANCHEZ THEN TO THE CRIME
SCENE.

00:16:39.297 --> 00:16:43.702 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: THEN POLICE
DISCOVERED THAT SANCHEZ'S REAL

00:16:43.735 --> 00:16:48.173 size:78% position:39%
TARGET THAT NIGHT WASN'T
MEGAN BARROSO AT ALL, BUT

00:16:48.206 --> 00:16:50.108 align:start position:0%
SOMEONE ELSE.

00:16:53.311 --> 00:16:56.915
&gt;&gt; Narrator: INVESTIGATORS
LEARNED THAT ON THE FOURTH OF

00:16:56.948 --> 00:17:00.285 align:start position:0%
JULY, VINCENT SANCHEZ HAD AN
ARGUMENT WITH A FORMER

00:17:00.318 --> 00:17:04.589
GIRLFRIEND, AND HE WAS ANGRY
BECAUSE SHE HADN'T INVITED HIM

00:17:04.622 --> 00:17:06.658 align:start position:0%
TO HER FAMILY PICNIC.

00:17:06.691 --> 00:17:11.863 align:start position:0% line:0%
&gt;&gt; WE THEORIZE HE TOOK THAT
AK-47, HE GOT IN HIS TRUCK, AND

00:17:11.896 --> 00:17:16.468 align:start position:0% line:0%
HE WAS PROBABLY OUT LOOKING FOR
HIS GIRLFRIEND.

00:17:16.501 --> 00:17:20.038 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: WHETHER HE PLANNED
TO USE THE WEAPON ON HIS

00:17:20.071 --> 00:17:23.108 align:start position:0%
GIRLFRIEND OR HER FAMILY IS
UNCLEAR.

00:17:23.141 --> 00:17:28.613
BUT ALONG THE WAY, INVESTIGATORS
BELIEVE SANCHEZ SAW MEGAN AT AN

00:17:28.646 --> 00:17:33.385 align:start position:0%
INTERSECTION, CHANGED HIS MIND,
AND DECIDED TO FOLLOW HER

00:17:33.418 --> 00:17:36.855 align:start position:0%
INSTEAD.

00:17:36.888 --> 00:17:44.329 align:start position:0%
THE EVIDENCE SHOWS SANCHEZ TRIED
TO GET MEGAN TO PULL OVER.

00:17:44.362 --> 00:17:47.165 align:start position:0%
HE THEN FIRED INTO MEGAN'S
BACKSEAT.

00:17:47.198 --> 00:18:00.312 align:start position:0%
[ GUNSHOT ]
AGAIN, MEGAN REFUSED TO STOP.

00:18:00.345 --> 00:18:06.184 align:start position:0%
SANCHEZ PULLED AHEAD OF HER, CUT
OFF HER PATH, AND STARTED

00:18:06.217 --> 00:18:12.491 align:start position:0%
SHOOTING.

00:18:12.524 --> 00:18:14.326 size:75% position:38%
MEGAN TRIED TO GET AWAY.

00:18:14.359 --> 00:18:17.262 align:start position:0%
SHE WAS HIT BY THE SHOT THROUGH
THE CAR DOOR.

00:18:17.295 --> 00:18:21.433
MEGAN MAY HAVE REACHED FOR HER
PHONE TO CALL FOR HELP, LOST

00:18:21.466 --> 00:18:31.576 align:start position:0%
CONTROL, AND HIT THE MEDIAN
BARRIER.

00:18:31.609 --> 00:18:40.318 align:start position:0%
SANCHEZ THEN ABDUCTED MEGAN AND
DROVE OFF.

00:18:40.351 --> 00:18:44.756 align:start position:0%
THE WHOLE TIME, SHE SHED THE
DISTINCTIVE RED GLITTER INTO HIS

00:18:44.789 --> 00:18:49.494 align:start position:0%
TRUCK, ONTO HIS RIFLE, AND ON
HER JACKET.

00:18:49.527 --> 00:18:54.199
MEDICAL EXPERTS BELIEVE MEGAN
WAS ALIVE WHEN SANCHEZ LEFT HER

00:18:54.232 --> 00:18:56.168 align:start position:0%
IN THE CANYON RAVINE.

00:18:56.201 --> 00:19:00.739
HE LEFT HER THERE WITHOUT HER
PANTS AND PROBABLY TOOK HER

00:19:00.772 --> 00:19:02.641 align:start position:0%
JACKET AS A TROPHY.

00:19:02.674 --> 00:19:07.312 line:0%
&gt;&gt; I COULDN'T GET AWAY FROM THE
IDEA THAT THIS HAD HAPPENED TO

00:19:07.345 --> 00:19:11.383 align:start position:0% line:0%
MY LITTLE GIRL -- THAT BEAUTIFUL
LITTLE GIRL WHO ALWAYS HAD A

00:19:11.416 --> 00:19:14.386 align:start position:0% line:0%
SMILE FOR ME, WHO ALWAYS GAVE
DAD A BIG HUG.

00:19:14.419 --> 00:19:15.554 align:start position:0% line:0%
I MISS HER HUGS.

00:19:15.587 --> 00:19:17.789 line:0%
TO THIS DAY, I MISS HER HUGS.

00:19:17.822 --> 00:19:23.595
&gt;&gt; Narrator: IN OCTOBER OF 2001,
SANCHEZ PLED GUILTY TO BEING THE

00:19:23.628 --> 00:19:28.200 size:88% position:44%
SIMI VALLEY RAPIST AND WAS
SENTENCED TO LIFE IN PRISON.

00:19:28.233 --> 00:19:32.804 align:start position:0%
HE ALSO PLED GUILTY TO MEGAN'S
MURDER.

00:19:32.837 --> 00:19:37.542 size:78% position:39%
SANCHEZ CLAIMED HE DIDN'T
SEXUALLY ASSAULT MEGAN.

00:19:37.575 --> 00:19:42.447 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; THE DEFENSE IN THIS CASE,
THEIR MAIN OBJECTIVE WAS TO SAVE

00:19:42.480 --> 00:19:44.616 size:81% position:41%
HIM FROM A DEATH SENTENCE.

00:19:44.649 --> 00:19:49.454 align:start position:0%
&gt;&gt; Narrator: BUT GIVEN SANCHEZ'S
PAST, JURORS CONCLUDED HE<i> DID</i>

00:19:49.487 --> 00:19:52.324 size:78% position:39%
SEXUALLY ASSAULT MEGAN...

00:19:52.357 --> 00:19:55.227 size:84% position:42%
AND SENTENCED HIM TO DEATH.

00:19:55.260 --> 00:19:56.895 size:75% position:38%
&gt;&gt; HE HAS NO CONSCIENCE.

00:19:56.928 --> 00:20:01.066
I HATE TO SAY HE'S AN ANIMAL
BECAUSE IT'S JUST -- IT'S TOO

00:20:01.099 --> 00:20:03.134
NICE OF A DESCRIPTION FOR HIM.

00:20:03.167 --> 00:20:07.405 line:0%
&gt;&gt; IT WAS JUST SO AMAZING, ALL
THE DETAIL AND THE AMOUNT OF

00:20:07.438 --> 00:20:11.509 line:0%
EFFORT THAT WENT INTO EACH
LITTLE PIECE OF THE PUZZLE OF

00:20:11.542 --> 00:20:13.778 line:0%
THE FORENSIC SCIENCE OF IT ALL.

00:20:13.811 --> 00:20:18.850
&gt;&gt; Narrator: NO ONE DOUBTS THAT
SANCHEZ WOULD HAVE CLAIMED MORE

00:20:18.883 --> 00:20:20.585 align:start position:0%
VICTIMS.

00:20:20.618 --> 00:20:25.457 size:88% position:44%
BUT A STRANGE COMBINATION OF
EVIDENCE, RANGING FROM LASER

00:20:25.490 --> 00:20:30.195 size:84% position:42%
BALLISTICS TO ANALYSIS OF A
CAR'S ON-BOARD COMPUTER TO

00:20:30.228 --> 00:20:34.499 align:start position:0%
SOMETHING AS SEEMINGLY
INSIGNIFICANT AS GLITTER, PROVED

00:20:34.532 --> 00:20:35.934 align:start position:0%
HIS GUILT.

00:20:35.967 --> 00:20:40.772 line:0%
&gt;&gt; IT WAS JUST AMAZING WHAT THE
CRIMINALISTS WERE ABLE TO DO AND

00:20:40.805 --> 00:20:45.176 align:start position:0% line:0%
THE EXPERTS WERE ABLE TO SAY TO
PUT TOGETHER A VERY VIVID

00:20:45.209 --> 00:20:49.347 align:start position:0% line:0%
PICTURE FOR THE JURY AS TO WHAT
HAPPENED OUT THERE.

00:20:49.380 --> 00:20:53.351 align:start position:0% line:0%
&gt;&gt; I WOULD SAY THE MOST
COMPELLING SCIENCE WAS THE

00:20:53.384 --> 00:20:57.956 align:start position:0% line:0%
BLOOD -- THE BLOOD FOUND IN
VINCENT'S VEHICLE, AND ALSO THE

00:20:57.989 --> 00:20:59.658 align:start position:0% line:0%
PIXIE GLITTER.

00:20:59.691 --> 00:21:03.428 align:start position:0% line:0%
THAT WAS AMAZING THAT THEY COULD
PUT THOSE PIECES OF PIXIE

00:21:03.461 --> 00:21:06.731 line:0%
GLITTER TOGETHER AND SHOW THAT
IT HAD BEEN LOCATED AT ALL THOSE

00:21:06.764 --> 00:21:10.035 align:start position:0% line:0%
DIFFERENT AREAS, AND IT WAS
CONSISTENT AMONGST EACH OTHER.

